<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= subject %></title>
    <style>
        /* Dark modern theme inspired by The VIP Studio dashboard */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d0f16; /* Dark background */
            color: #e5e7eb; /* Light text */
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #151821; /* Slightly lighter dark */
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #fcd45b; /* Yellow header */
            color: #0d0f16;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #d1d5db;
        }

        .otp-display {
            background-color: #1f232d;
            border: 1px solid #2d313d;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fcd45b; /* Yellow color for OTP */
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: #0d0f16;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #fcd45b;
        }

        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #1f232d;
            border-left: 4px solid #fcd45b;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #fcd45b;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .instructions {
            background-color: #1f232d;
            border: 1px solid #2d313d;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .instructions p {
            color: #fcd45b;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .instructions ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #d1d5db;
        }

        .instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .warning {
            background-color: #1f232d;
            border-left: 4px solid #fcd45b;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #fcd45b;
        }

        .warning p {
            color: #fcd45b;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .warning ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #d1d5db;
        }

        .warning li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #11131a;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #2d313d;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 24px;
                letter-spacing: 6px;
                padding: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <%= companyName %> account. Use the OTP code below to verify your identity:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-display">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #fcd45b;">Your One-Time Password (OTP):</p>
                <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="expiry-notice">
                ⚠️ This OTP will expire in <%= expiryTime %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <p>Instructions:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Enter this OTP on the password reset page</li>
                    <li>Create a new strong password</li>
                    <li>Login with your new credentials</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <p>Security Notice:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Never share this OTP with anyone</li>
                    <li>Our team will never ask for your OTP</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this reset, please ignore this email and ensure your account is secure</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>If you need assistance, contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The <%= companyName %> Team</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>